# Quiz Game Application

## Overview

This project is an interactive Quiz Game Application developed during the SkillCraft Technology Web Development Internship. Users can answer multiple-choice questions and receive a score at the end.

## Features

- Multiple-choice questions
- Interactive user interface
- Score calculation
- Dynamic question display
- Responsive design

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

## Project Structure

Task-03-Quiz-Game
│
├── index.html
├── style.css
├── script.js
└── assets

## How to Run

1. Download or clone repository
2. Open project folder
3. Run `index.html`

## Learning Outcomes

- JavaScript logic building
- Dynamic content rendering
- Event handling
- User interaction design

